itemProp="url" content="https:////zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/28564030"/><meta itemProp="datePublished" content="2017-08-16T13:41:27.000Z"/><meta itemProp="dateModified" content="2017-08-16T13:41:26.000Z"/><meta itemProp="commentCount" content="469"/><meta itemProp="image" content="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-068a9756bdb9622f7d93c739c023e19a_hd.jpg"/><div class="RichContent is-collapsed"><div class="RichContent-cover"><div class="RichContent-cover-inner"><div class="VagueImage" data-src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-068a9756bdb9622f7d93c739c023e19a_400x224.jpg"><div class="VagueImage-mask is-active"></div></div></div></div><div class="RichContent-inner"><span class="RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText" itemProp="articleBody">举世闻名的兵马俑坑只是秦始皇为自己修建的众多陪葬坑中的一处。你知道他老人家修了多少陪葬坑吗？已经发现的就超过180座！此外，还有数百座陪葬墓和数百万平方米的陵寝建筑基址！只可惜，秦陵绝大多数陪葬坑并不对外开放。绝大多数出土文物，普通观众根本无缘见到——就连我也没见过！这些文物要么只在临时展览中露面，要么根本就没离开过实验室和库房。所以，本人特别奉上资料图片，帮大家弥补遗憾，开开眼界！一、石甲胄坑 （…</span><button type="button" class="Button ContentItem-more Button--plain">阅读全文<span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--ArrowDown ContentItem-arrowIcon" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24"><path d="M12 13L8.285 9.218a.758.758 0 0 0-1.064 0 .738.738 0 0 0 0 1.052l4.249 4.512a.758.758 0 0 0 1.064 0l4.246-4.512a.738.738 0 0 0 0-1.052.757.757 0 0 0-1.063 0L12.002 13z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></button></div><div class="ContentItem-actions"><span><button aria-label="赞同" type="button" class="Button VoteButton VoteButton--up"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--TriangleUp VoteButton-TriangleUp" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="10" height="10"><path d="M2 18.242c0-.326.088-.532.237-.896l7.98-13.203C10.572 3.57 11.086 3 12 3c.915 0 1.429.571 1.784 1.143l7.98 13.203c.15.364.236.57.236.896 0 1.386-.875 1.9-1.955 1.9H3.955c-1.08 0-1.955-.517-1.955-1.9z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span>赞同 <!-- -->7.4K</button><button aria-label="